---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout title="Careers with Inguz Care" description="Values-led careers in residential children’s care.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Careers with Inguz Care</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg">
      We’re building a steady, values-led team. There are no live vacancies right now, but opportunities will be
      posted here as our services grow.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-2xl border p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Stay in touch</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        If you’re passionate about warm, trauma-informed care and would like us to keep your details on file for future
        roles, please send a brief note about your experience and interests.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-4 inline-block px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#5f7c7b] text-white font-semibold hover:bg-[#3d5756]">
        Register your interest
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-slate-600">
      We are an equal opportunities employer and welcome applications from all backgrounds and lived experiences.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
